{"tid":2096451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"竟然有一條女係我想同佢拍拖多過扑嘢","createTime":"2020-07-06T06:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T06:40:51.000Z","uid":308264,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"822817171d77472db7fe0611d08d420789628d7c","tid":2096451,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />通常一見到靚女就會鍾意 <br />\n但係近排竟然見到一個我唔識得點樣形容嘅女仔<br />\n我馬上對佢一見鍾情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係今次竟然唔係想扑嘢而係想同佢拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未見到佢個人淨係見到佢條褲就已經認到係佢<br />\n仲要即刻面紅 每日見一次已經夠<br />\n<br />\n甚至同佢連野都未講過 唔通呢一種就真係叫做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f2f8ed5d3f98ebc06fab1ece27d47bbbc0a97f","tid":2096451,"uid":300529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"係 你都係想人咁答"},{"pid":"96db7baa76f8d80551ad84c276de5299f3f5306d","tid":2096451,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"60791f1a4b2658a892efd699d7f8d3fd393825c3","tid":2096451,"uid":202151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:32:07.000Z","msg":"但係佢覺得你好柒"},{"pid":"13d9b8b4611a2601843ea65c7486251fc18337d5","tid":2096451,"uid":193642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"證明你開始性無能"},{"pid":"0363b6a420e0d044d62bb517684b32e7e7774a09","tid":2096451,"uid":107605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e3fd7b0c6b80f3bde974dbff0500d3bb391800","tid":2096451,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"證明你有病"},{"pid":"19b01f175315fffefbf50594658a949bc5289f4b","tid":2096451,"uid":308264,"like":0